  "body": "Currently tests are using: `MockSentry.InsertChain -> insertPoS -> StageLoopIteration`\r\nAs a result - existing tests do not test UpdateForkChoice logic and can't catch bugs in UpdateForkChoice. \r\n\r\nI fixed couple bugs in updateForkChoice:\r\n- pruning was missed \r\n- erigon3 `rawdbv3.TxNums.Truncate` was called wrong way - existed some tests\r\n\r\nI understand that UpdateForkChoice is not compatible - and changing a lot. But it make sense to adopt at-least some existing tests (for example `jsonrpc` package tests) to use UpdateForkChoice. \r\n",
